        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1705",
        "content": "It was very well for Margaret that the extreme quiet of the Harley Street house, during Edith's recovery from her confinement, gave her the natural rest which she needed.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
