        "content": "But I thought that it might be the effect of the antiquities of Oxford.'",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1705_142318_000031_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1705/142318/1705_142318_000031_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1705",
        "content": "In Oxford, I could have managed all the landlords in the place, and had my own way, with half the trouble your Milton landlord has given me, and defeated me after all.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1705_142318_000031_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1705/142318/1705_142318_000031_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1705",
        "content": "Luckily, mr Thornton found a tenant for it.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1705_142318_000031_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1705/142318/1705_142318_000031_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1705",
        "content": "Why don't you ask after mr Thornton, Margaret?",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1705_142318_000031_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1705/142318/1705_142318_000031_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1705",
        "content": "Taken more than half the trouble off my hands.'",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1705_142318_000032_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1705/142318/1705_142318_000032_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1705",
        "content": "How is mrs Thornton?' asked Margaret hurriedly and below her breath, though she tried to speak out.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1705_142318_000033_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1705/142318/1705_142318_000033_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1705",
        "content": "'I suppose they're well.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1705_142318_000033_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1705/142318/1705_142318_000033_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1705",
        "content": "I've been staying at their house till I was driven out of it by the perpetual clack about that Thornton girl's marriage.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1705_142318_000033_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1705/142318/1705_142318_000033_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1705",
        "content": "It was too much for Thornton himself, though she was his sister.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1705_142318_000033_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1705/142318/1705_142318_000033_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1705",
        "content": "He's getting past the age for caring for such things, either as principal or accessory.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1705_142318_000033_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1705/142318/1705_142318_000033_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1705",
        "content": "I thought mrs Thornton had been made of sterner stuff.'",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1705_142318_000035_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1705/142318/1705_142318_000035_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1705",
        "content": "'Perhaps so.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1705_142318_000035_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1705/142318/1705_142318_000035_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1705",
        "content": "You've studied her, have you?",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1705_142318_000036_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1705/142318/1705_142318_000036_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1705",
        "content": "'I know it,' said Margaret.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1705_142318_000036_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1705/142318/1705_142318_000036_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1705",
        "content": "'Oh, here is tea at last!' exclaimed she, as if relieved.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1705_142318_000036_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1705/142318/1705_142318_000036_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1705",
        "content": "She could hardly tell what to say at first, and was thankful for all the tea table occupations, which gave her an excuse for keeping silence, and him an opportunity of recovering himself.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1705_142318_000036_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1705/142318/1705_142318_000036_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1705",
        "content": "For, to tell the truth, he had rather forced himself up to Harley Street this evening, with a view of getting over an awkward meeting, awkward even in the presence of Captain Lennox and Edith, and doubly awkward now that he found her the only lady there, and the person to whom he must naturally and perforce address a great part of his conversation.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1705_142318_000036_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1705/142318/1705_142318_000036_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1705",
        "content": "She began to talk on the subject which came uppermost in her mind, after the first flush of awkward shyness.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1705_142318_000039_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1705/142318/1705_142318_000039_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1705",
        "content": "mr Lennox has discovered that he sailed for Australia only last August; only two months before Frederick was in England, and gave us the names of---- '",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1705_142318_000040_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1705/142318/1705_142318_000040_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1705",
        "content": "'Frederick in England! you never told me that!' exclaimed mr Bell in surprise.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1705_142318_000041_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1705/142318/1705_142318_000041_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1705",
        "content": "I never doubted you had been told.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1705_142318_000041_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1705/142318/1705_142318_000041_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1705",
        "content": "Of course, it was a great secret, and perhaps I should not have named it now,' said Margaret, a little dismayed.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1705_142318_000042_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1705/142318/1705_142318_000042_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1705",
        "content": "'I have never named it to either my brother or your cousin,' said mr Lennox, with a little professional dryness of implied reproach.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1705_142318_000043_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1705/142318/1705_142318_000043_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1705",
        "content": "I am not living in a talking, babbling world, nor yet among people who are trying to worm facts out of me; you needn't look so frightened because you have let the cat out of the bag to a faithful old hermit like me.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1705_142318_000043_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1705/142318/1705_142318_000043_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1705",
        "content": "Stay!' (interrupting himself rather abruptly) 'was it at your mother's funeral?'",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1705_142318_000045_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1705/142318/1705_142318_000045_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1705",
        "content": "'To be sure!",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1705_142318_000045_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1705/142318/1705_142318_000045_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1705",
        "content": "To be sure!",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1705_142318_000045_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1705/142318/1705_142318_000045_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1705",
        "content": "Why, some one asked me if he had not been over then, and I denied it stoutly-not many weeks ago-who could it have been?",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1705_142318_000047_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1705/142318/1705_142318_000047_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1705",
        "content": "There was a pause for a moment or two.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1705_142318_000048_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1705/142318/1705_142318_000048_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1705",
        "content": "Cannot you come here?",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1705_142318_000049_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1705/142318/1705_142318_000049_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1705",
        "content": "But I will certainly come if you wish it,' replied mr Lennox, with a little afterthought of extreme willingness, which made Margaret shrink into herself, and almost wish that she had not proposed her natural request.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1705_142318_000049_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1705/142318/1705_142318_000049_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1705",
        "content": "mr Bell got up and looked around him for his hat, which had been removed to make room for tea.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1705_142318_000051_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1705/142318/1705_142318_000051_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1705",
        "content": "'I believe I shall stay and see my brother and sister,' said mr Lennox, making no movement of departure.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1705_142318_000052_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1705/142318/1705_142318_000052_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1705",
        "content": "'I want you to see Edith; and I want Edith to know you.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1705_142318_000053_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1705/142318/1705_142318_000053_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1705",
        "content": "I suppose I am not much to \"see,\" eh, Margaret?'",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1705_142318_000054_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1705/142318/1705_142318_000054_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1705",
        "content": "He joked, to give her time to recover from the slight flutter which he had detected in her manner on his proposal to leave; and she caught the tone, and threw the ball back.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1705_142318_000054_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1705/142318/1705_142318_000054_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1705",
        "content": "To be sure, in her quiet black dress, she was a contrast to Edith, dancing in her white crape mourning, and long floating golden hair, all softness and glitter.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1705_142318_000054_000003",
